Package: skindiff
Title: Numerical Simulation of Drug Diffusion Through Skin
Version: 0.6.0
Authors@R: person("Dominik", "Selzer", email = "d.selzer@scientific-consilience.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Solves the one-dimensional diffusion equation through a stack of
    skin compartments (vehicle / stratum corneum / deeper skin layers / sink)
    using a Crank-Nicolson finite-difference scheme. Returns time-resolved mass
    in each compartment together with concentration-depth profiles.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports:
    Rcpp (>= 1.0.0)
LinkingTo:
    Rcpp
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
SystemRequirements: C++17
Config/testthat/edition: 3
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
